title: BREAKING: Shots Reportedly Fired Outside of British Parliament, Multiple Injuries
text:
There are multiple reports of a shooting outside of the British Parliament in London. Reports of shots fired outside UK Parliament, Palace of Westminster reportedly in lockdown https://t.co/G8wSRu5JHX — BBC Breaking News (@BBCBreaking) March 22, 2017 
This is a breaking story, stay tuned for updates.
